0%;"><section style=" margin: 15px 0%;  "><section style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;" class=""><br></section></section></section></section></section><p><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px; color: #4F6128;">ღ &nbsp;设备先进：</span><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px;">引进美国顶尖检测仪器，罗氏雅培全自动免疫发光仪；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px; color: #4F6128;">ღ &nbsp;早期筛查：</span><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px;">比常规检测早3-5年发现肿瘤病灶；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px; color: #4F6128;">ღ &nbsp;病毒排查：</span><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px;">在人体无症状期超早期发现病毒携带；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px; color: #4F6128;">ღ &nbsp;病源追踪：</span><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px;">通过肺病易感基因检测，评估肺部原始致病原因；</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p><section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="32290" style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="clear: both; border: 0px none; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-top-width: 2.5px; border-top-style: solid; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); font-size: 1em; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(254, 254, 254); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border: 0px rgb(128, 177, 53); margin-top: 2px; overflow: hidden; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="" data-bcless="darken" data-brushtype="text" style="display: inline-block; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 5px 10px; height: 32px; vertical-align: top; font-family: inherit; font-weight: bold; float: left; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(71, 98, 29); box-sizing: border-box !important; background: rgb(128, 177, 53);"><p class=""><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 站酷高端黑;">肺癌家族史与肺癌发病风险显著增加相关</span></p></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 0px; height: 0px; border-top-width: 32px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(128, 177, 53); border-right-width: 32px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: transparent; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 2px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p class=""><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑;">肺部疾病包括哮喘、感染性疾病如流感、肺炎和肺结核，慢性阻塞性肺病（COPD）等。其中肺癌作为全球头号癌症杀手，已经上升到全球第一高发的恶性肿瘤。近年来的发病率在全国内</span><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; line-height: inherit;">呈持续上升趋势，其发病率和死亡率均位居肿瘤排行第一。肺部疾病还容易诱发如糖尿病、冠心病、脑中风、恶性肿瘤等，其最终直接死亡原因往往是肺部感染和呼吸衰竭！</span></span></p><p class=""><br></p><p class=""><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑;">肺癌不是遗传疾病，但是大量的数据显示有肺癌聚集的家族，其子女患肺癌的几率比一般人高出几倍。国外研究机构对超过10.2万名日本中老年人展开了长达13年的追踪调查，他们中共出</span><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; line-height: inherit;">现了791例肺癌。研究表明直系亲属有肺癌患者是直系亲属没有肺癌患者患病率的2倍。肺癌的遗传性在女性身上表现得尤为明显。肺癌患者中至少有10%的人具有遗传性，母亲患有肺癌，</span></span></p><p class=""><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px;">遗传给子女的机会要比父亲高出2-3倍。</span></p><p class=""><span style="font-family: 站酷高端黑; font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p><section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="90144" style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="rgb(128, 177, 53)" data-custom="rgb(128, 177, 53)"><section style=" display:flex; text-align: center; margin: 10px 0%; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);-ms-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); "><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; flex:0 0 20%;"><section style=" margin: 15px 0%;  "><section style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;" class=""></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; flex:0 0 60%;"><section style=" margin-right: 0%; margin-left: 0%;  "><section style="display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 7px; margin-top: 7px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(128, 177, 53);"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border: 2px solid rgb(128, 177, 53); padding: 2px 8px; font-size: 12px; margin: -7px 5px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 2; color: rgb(128, 177, 53); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p class=""><span class="">&nbsp; &nbsp; 项目意义 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; flex:0 0 20%;"><section style=" margin: 15px 0%;  "><section style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;" class=""><br></section></section></section></section></section><p class=""><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 站酷高端黑;">1.病毒的潜伏期较长，一般肺部疾病及呼吸道疾病均是病毒感染后诱发的症状。</span></p><p class=""><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 站酷高端黑;">2.病毒的种类和突变率持续升高，新型病毒感染已经广泛存在，一旦出现肺部疾病症状，医院无法及时救治。</span></p><p class=""><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 站酷高端黑;">3.从基因和遗传学的层面，提早了解肺部疾病的患病风险。</span></p>
